"type":"text","text":"Input: x вҲҲ в„қ^D (high-dimensional, e.g., D = 784 for 28Г—28 image)\n    вҶ“\nEncoder: Maps x through layers with decreasing dimensions\n    вҶ“\nBottleneck: z вҲҲ в„қ^d where d < D (low-dimensional latent vector)\n    вҶ“\nDecoder: Maps z through layers with increasing dimensions\n    вҶ“\nOutput: x' вҲҲ в„қ^D (reconstructed input)"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"The bottleneck layer's "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"output is the latent vector "},{"type":"inlineMath","attrs":{"latex":"z"}},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":":\n\\[\nz = \\text{encoder}(x)\n\\]\n\\[\nx' = \\text{decoder}(z)\n\\]"}]},{"type":"horizontalRule"},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":2},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Key Characteristics"}]},{"type":"table","content":[{"type":"tableRow","content":[{"type":"tableHeader","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Property"}]}]},{"type":"tableHeader","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Description"}]}]}]},{"type":"tableRow","content":[{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Smallest dimension"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Most narrow part of network (e.g., 32 units vs 784 input)"}]}]}]},{"type":"tableRow","content":[{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Latent representation"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","conte